Common.Highlight.Common.Text: For Sale via Expressions of Interest

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
As exclusive agents, CBRE are excited to present to market for sale via Expressions of Interest, 75 Proprietary Street, Tingalpa. In an extremely tightly held and sought after industrial market, this opportunity is one not to miss. Tingalpa is located approx. 11 radial kilometres east of the Brisbane CBD and is situated just off main Wynnum Road offering excellent access to the Gateway Motorway (approx. 800m of the entrance).

With limited available options, this is a rare opportunity to secure a quality, fully refurbished office/warehouse freestander. This property appeals to both owner occupiers or investors looking to secure a prime facility located in the a blue chip precinct.

Some of the salient features of this opportunity include;

•	2,084sqm regular shaped GI allotment
•	1,607sqm office/warehouse facility
•	Highbay, clearspan warehouse accessed via standard electric container height roller door
•	Full kitchen & amenities on both levels
•	Full refurbished facility both internally & externally
•	Great off street parking

Expressions of interest closing 18th August 2021 at 3pm.

For further information on this opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please don’t hesitate to contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons of CBRE.

CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale, via an expression of interest campaign, 246 New Cleveland Road, Tingalpa. This corporate, 1,457sqm freestanding office/warehouse is situated just off Manly Road in the heart of Tingalpa. One of the most highly sought after & rapidly developing industrial precincts in Brisbane, Tingalpa offers excellent connectivity. The property is located within minutes’ drive to the Gateway Motorway connecting greater Brisbane, approximately 13kms from the CBD and within close proximity to ample amenity.

Some the features of this opportunity include;

•	Currently leased until 31/03/2022
•	Would appeal to any owner occupier or investor
•	377sqm* office accommodation split over two levels
•	1,080sqm* highbay, clearspan warehouse
•	Accessed via two (2) electric container roller doors 
•	Kitchen & amenities located on both office levels
•	Fully fenced and secured site

Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 13th May at 12pm (AEST) *** If not sold prior

For further information on this opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Ben Lyons of CBRE today.

* Adjacent the Gateway Motorway for ease of access north and south

* Loading docks with dock levellers including 8 docks for rigid vehicles and 4 docks for articulated vehicles
